#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:2
msgid "Wi-Fi"
msgstr "Wi-Fi"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:6
msgid "Wi-Fi又称“无线热点”或“无线网络”，是Wi-Fi联盟的商标，一个基于IEEE 802.11标准的无线局域网技术。"
msgstr "Wi-Fi, also known as a wireless hotspot or wireless network, is a trademark of the Wi-Fi Alliance and a wireless LAN technology based on the IEEE 802.11 standard."

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:9
msgid "攻击"
msgstr "Attacks"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:12
msgid "暴力破解"
msgstr "Brute Force"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:13
msgid "WiFi密码是基于预置的秘钥，可以通过抓取报文的方式在本地快速的批量进行密码爆破尝试。"
msgstr "Wi-Fi passwords are based on pre-shared keys. After capturing packets, an attacker can quickly perform bulk password brute-force attempts locally."

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:16
msgid "伪造热点"
msgstr "Fake Hotspots"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:17
msgid "AP可以动态的广播自己，客户也可以主动发送探针请求。可以伪造AP发送对探针请求的响应包，来让客户端错误的识别。"
msgstr "An AP can dynamically broadcast itself, and clients can also actively send probe requests. A forged AP can send responses to those probe requests and cause clients to identify it incorrectly."

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:20
msgid "秘钥重装攻击"
msgstr "Key Reinstallation Attacks"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:21
msgid "该漏洞由Vanhoef发现。Wi-Fi在握手时双方会更新秘钥，该攻击通过重放握手信息，令客户端重新安装相同的秘钥。"
msgstr "This vulnerability was discovered by Vanhoef. During a Wi-Fi handshake, both sides update keys; this attack replays handshake messages so that the client reinstalls the same key."

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:24
msgid "Dragonblood"
msgstr "Dragonblood"

#: ../../source/network/wifi.rst:25
msgid "最新版的WPA3标准在实现上存在一些问题，同样由Vanhoef发现。包含拒绝服务攻击、降级攻击、侧信道泄露等。"
msgstr "The latest WPA3 standard had several implementation issues, also discovered by Vanhoef, including denial-of-service attacks, downgrade attacks, and side-channel leaks."

